('Shaunia', 'If you’re feeling lonely, a quick walk or a favorite hobby can help lift your mood.', 'loneliness'),
('Shaunia', 'Here’s a tip: celebrate small wins, like finishing a book or trying a new recipe.', 'achievement'),
('Shaunia', 'Board games, puzzles, or learning a new skill are great ways to spend time with others.', 'activities'),
('Shaunia', 'Online communities like Meetup or Reddit can help you connect with people who share your interests.', 'community'),
('Shaunia', 'If you have a disagreement, listening calmly and sharing your feelings can help resolve things.', 'conflict_resolution'),
('Shaunia', 'Remember to take care of yourself—rest, eat well, and enjoy the little things.', 'self_care'),
('Shaunia', 'You’re always welcome to chat with me if you need a friendly ear!', 'support');
